@startuml

actor User
participant "Angular Frontend" as Frontend
participant "Spring Boot Backend" as Backend
participant "LwM2M Server" as LwM2MServer
participant "Bootstrap Server" as BootstrapServer
participant "LwM2M Client" as LwM2MClient
participant "Ethereum Blockchain" as Blockchain

User -> Frontend : Access application
Frontend -> Backend : Authenticate (JWT)
Backend -> Blockchain : Verify user (UserStore)
Blockchain --> Backend : User verified
Backend --> Frontend : JWT token

User -> Frontend : Monitor LwM2M clients
Frontend -> Backend : Request client data
Backend -> LwM2MServer : Fetch client info
LwM2MServer --> Backend : Client data
Backend -> Blockchain : Retrieve client details (ClientStore)
Blockchain --> Backend : Client details
Backend --> Frontend : Combined client data

User -> Frontend : Trigger temperature analysis
Frontend -> Backend : Request analysis
Backend -> LwM2MServer : Request temperature data
LwM2MServer -> LwM2MClient : Read temperature
LwM2MClient --> LwM2MServer : Temperature data
LwM2MServer --> Backend : Temperature data
Backend -> Backend : Detect anomaly
Backend -> Blockchain : Store anomaly (AnomalyStore)
Blockchain --> Backend : Anomaly stored
Backend --> Frontend : Anomaly notification

LwM2MClient -> BootstrapServer : Request bootstrap
BootstrapServer -> Blockchain : Fetch security info (ClientStore)
Blockchain --> BootstrapServer : Security configuration
BootstrapServer --> LwM2MClient : Bootstrap data
LwM2MClient -> LwM2MServer : Register

@enduml